An Event Driven Simulation Framework for Java
See user-manual.pdf in this directory for details.

Licensed under AGPL V 3.0

Requires Java 1.7 and Maven 3.x

To build:

	cd <top level directory>
	mvn clean install
	
To build eclipse plugin:

	cd eclipse-integration
	mvn clean install

## Maven configuration

For snapshots, include the hellblazer snapshot repository:

	<repository>
	    <id>hellblazer-snapshots</id>
	    <url>https://repository-hal900000.forge.cloudbees.com/snapshot/</url>
	</repository>

	<plugin-repository>
	    <id>hellblazer-plugin-snapshots</id>
	    <url>https://repository-hal900000.forge.cloudbees.com/snapshot/</url>
	</plugin-repository>

### Prime Mover Runtime

The artifact required for simulation runtime

	<dependency>
	    <groupId>com.hellblazer</groupId>
	    <artifactId>primeMover</artifactId>
	    <version>0.0.5-SNAPSHOT</version>
	</dependency>

### Prime Mover Maven Plugin

The plugin required to transform simulation code

	<plugin>
	    <groupId>com.hellblazer.primeMover</groupId>
	    <artifactId>maven.plugin</artifactId>
	    <version>0.0.5-SNAPSHOT</version>
	    <executions>
	        <execution> 
	            <goals>
	                <goal>transform</goal> 
	                <goal>transform-test</goal> 
	            </goals>
	        </execution>
	    </executions>
	</plugin>
